Dependencies:
  ghc; cmdargs; DrIFT; HaXml;

To install GHC refer to:
  http://www.haskell.org/ghc/distribution_packages

Install monad transformer library (Ubuntu):
  suod apt-get install libghc-mtl-dev

To install cmdargs execute:
  cabal install cmdargs

If you have no cabal then installt it (Ubuntu):
  sudo apt-get install cabal-install
  cabal update

Install DrIFT from http://repetae.net/computer/haskell/DrIFT/ or your system package manage

To install HaXml execute:
  cabal install HaXml-1.20
Please note that there are some problems with recent version of HaXml and DrIFT. This is why we use an older one.

Once the libraries are in place, compile the translator:
  make